title: New: jumpswim❀ – Do For Love (Feat. Ninna Lundberg)
content: Denmark’s Ninna Lundberg cropped up last year with her stunning track, Fall Out Of Love, a blog and Hype Machine favourite. Now twelve months down the line, she’s lent her vocals to Do For Love, this fantastic first outing from South London’s jumpswim❀ (Jordan Randhawa). Recorded on relatively basic equipment, it’s a bold, soulful number, perfect for those lazy evenings. Check it out below.
